
## Initial Scope (MVP)

### Venue Discovery & Requests

* User authentication
* Browse available venues
* View calendar availability
* Select date and time slots
* Send booking requests to venues

### Venue Management

* Venue authentication
* Accept / decline requests
* Add venue information
* Publish monthly availability
* Remove availability entries

## Planned Improvements

* Subscription model
* Search and filtering
* City-based discovery
* Calendar editing tools
* Request management improvements

## Status

Early-stage prototype currently under active development.
Features and scope may evolve over time.
